{"id": "EUVD-2024-51297", "enisaUuid": "1337b472-c056-33c0-a16b-dd6eb121f9a8", "description": "An issue was discovered in GitLab CE/EE affecting all versions starting from 16.4 prior to 17.5.5, starting from 17.6 prior to 17.6.3, and starting from 17.7 prior to 17.7.1. When a user is created via the SAML provider, the external groups setting overrides the external provider configuration. As a result, the user may not be marked as external thereby giving those users access to internal projects or groups.", "datePublished": "2025-01-09T06:33:13", "dateUpdated": "2025-01-09T15:29:59", "baseScore": 4.2, "baseScoreVersion": "3.1", "baseScoreVector": "CVSS:3.1/AV:N/AC:H/PR:L/UI:N/S:U/C:L/I:L/A:N", "references": ["https://gitlab.com/gitlab-org/gitlab/-/issues/479165", "https://about.gitlab.com/releases/2025/01/08/patch-release-gitlab-17-7-1-released/#instance-saml-does-not-respect-external_provider-configuration"], "aliases": ["CVE-2024-13041"], "assigner": "GitLab", "epss": 0.03, "enisaIdProduct": [{"id": "10df17d9-a032-320e-bee6-9c606a6333e0", "product": {"name": "GitLab"}, "product_version": "16.4 <17.5.5"}, {"id": "616cbd61-c5d1-353f-bfc2-b70f61737fe6", "product": {"name": "GitLab"}, "product_version": "17.7 <17.7.1"}, {"id": "d15d4da7-0f75-34e7-8e5d-c67d22401d07", "product": {"name": "GitLab"}, "product_version": "17.6 <17.6.3"}], "enisaIdVendor": [{"id": "8740f7be-ad92-3f15-a9a2-5e6c1e51b640", "vendor": {"name": "GitLab"}}], "isExploited": false}